For the entire world the following visualisation presents the estimates and UN-projections of the remaining expected life years for 10-year-olds. The rise ‚Äì best visible on the Map-view ‚Äì shows that the increasing life expectancy is not only due to declining child mortality, but that mortality at higher ages also declined globally.

